  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      after advent of RD photoreceptor degeneration Occurred. This process appears as a incredible
      and progressive event that will not stop till reattachment of RPE and neurosensory retina
      happened .

      Process of degeneration begins from first hours of RD establishment Neuroprotection of
      photoreceptor following RD is a novel and debatable discussion encountered in recent years .

      How to stop this phenomena and neuroprotective agent role in this issue are a new interest of
      researches.

      In the study investigators are planning to perform a clinical trial to demonstrate the
      minocycline neuroprotective effect in a double blind design as this impact has been
      implicated previously in a animal study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
